@node "JIMMY WHITE'S WHIRLWIND SNOOKER"
JIMMY WHITE'S WHIRLWIND SNOOKER

Enter Trick Shot mode.  At any time on the table press the 'F7' key followed
by the 'F4' key and finally the 'F1' key.  A double click sound will be heard.
Return to the Control menu and access the Demo mode menu - there should be a
third option - DO A RANDOM 147 BREAK.  Select it and watch the computer
perform 147 breaks all day long.
@endnode
@node "JOHN MADDEN'S AMERICAN FOOTBALL"
JOHN MADDEN'S AMERICAN FOOTBALL

To get the ball back when you're kicking off (all the time with some teams).
When the kicking meter is on the screen put the direction full to the right
with no power at all.  Cincinnati, Kansas, All Madden, and Minnesota can get
the ball all the time.

Passwords:

    0540300 - Quarter final
    0150361 - Semi final
    0550361 - Super bowl final
@endnode
@node "JUDGE DREDD"
JUDGE DREDD

Log on computer as "DREDD" then type in "BRUCKEN PLAYING HERO QUEST" (NOTE:
possibly no space in "HEROQUEST")  followed by the 'RETURN' key, and exit.
The 'Help' key can now be used to skip levels.
@endnode
